Ernest Thesiger https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ernest_Thesiger 0 Ernest Frederic Graham Thesiger, CBE (15 January 1879 – 14 January 1961) was an English stage and film actor. He is noted for his performance as Doctor Septimus Pretorius in James Whale's film Bride of Frankenstein (1935).
